  "title": "New website review",
  "body": "Awesome job on the new documentation & website 👍  I really like the new getting started & guides 💯 \r\n\r\nA few minor issues I've spotted:\r\n\r\n - [x] Would love to have a sticky left menu\r\n - [x] Wondering whether we should push ES6 syntax or not in examples?\r\n - [x] the DocSearch implementation is still referencing the Android index :)\r\n - [x] Homepage's hero is not responsive\r\n - [x] On the `/instantsearch.html` page, the markdown is broken:\r\n\r\n![screen shot 2017-05-10 at 08 51 38](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/29529/25886472/ffb8a9b8-355d-11e7-923c-8049539c9157.png)\r\n",
